	<l>smaraniṁ beṁdurivaṁge rōgatatiyiṁdaṁ noṁdaḷalvaṁge ni </l>
	<l>ṣṭhuramugraṁ kaluṣaṁgaḷiṁ baḷalvavaṁgatyugratāpaṁgaḷiṁ </l>
	<l>koraguttaḷkuvavaṁge śatrubhayadiṁ bēḷāgi bīḷvaṁge sā</l>
