	<l>ppaḍada śarīrigaḷ tr̥ṇada hāhegaḷakkaṭa maṇṇa boṁbegaḷ ‌</l>
	<l>kuḍuvuve bēḍu bēḍolidudīva mahānidhiyaṁ mahēśanaṁ </l>
	<l>mr̥ḍanananūnadāniyanalaṁpina peṁpina haṁpeyāḷdanaṁ</l>
